channel.title: A problem I can't seem to pass.. Please help!
channel.description:
Hello, I've just recently started a new server.. Well tried.
I did everything right..Or so I think, After many days of trying to get my compiler to work, I finally got it, But I still can't log in.. It just takes a really long time then says Error connecting to server..
Can someone tell me what I did wrong..
My port forward thing is
RSPS, 43594-43594 both 192.168.1.2 enabled.
It would be soooo nice if someone could help me with this problem.
